WEBVTT

00:00:07.712 --> 00:00:12.592
In the 7th century CE, 
one man started a chain of events

00:00:12.592 --> 00:00:14.927
that would change
the world order for good.

00:00:15.428 --> 00:00:19.474
The prophet Muhammad united the people
of the Arabian Peninsula

00:00:19.474 --> 00:00:21.476
through the formation of Islam.

00:00:21.893 --> 00:00:25.354
These people included both 
nomadic Bedouin tribes

00:00:25.354 --> 00:00:28.941
and the inhabitants of oasis cities
like Mecca and Medina.

00:00:29.317 --> 00:00:34.280
Until Muhammad’s time, the region 
